race.comment: GRINZINGER POD (12) will be better for his placings as favourite at Caulfield Heath and Cranbourne. Finds easier grade and has more up the sleeve. Well placed to take this out. STREET CONQUEROR (7) went close at Warrnambool and is also back in grade. Won a 66 prior and hits this at peak. Maps well and is a player. PANO'S PRIDE (3) is third-up and will find this more suitable than Flemington last time. Has more to give and races forward. The 2kg claim brings him into it. OLATUNDE (16) resumes and won on the Ballarat synthetic by a big space at his only fresh outing. Has the blinkers on for the first time and Coffey sticks from the recent Echuca trial win. Keep very safe. ZEMGRINDA (4) is racing well and draws to get every chance. In the mix.
